OL,3,CWorld's first amusement park among
OL,4,CVictorian building on 'endangered' list
OL,6,FFrom a 19th century school building in
OL,7,FLondon to an iconic amusement park in
OL,8,FSouthend-on-Sea, the Victorian Society
OL,9,Freveal 'endangered' buildings
OL,11,FThe world's first purpose-built
OL,12,Famusement park is among other
OL,13,Fbuildings that have been placed on a
OL,14,Fmost "endangered" list due to the
OL,15,F"terrifying" state they have been left
OL,16,Fin.
