OL,3,CWorld's first amusement park among
OL,4,CVictorian building on 'endangered' list
OL,6,FMaking Victorian Society's annual top
OL,7,Ften list of buildings and structures
OL,8,Fare a 19th-century banqueting hall for
OL,9,Findustrial labourers and the Kursaal
OL,10,Fin Southend-on-Sea, Essex, which is
OL,11,Fbelieved to be the world's first
OL,12,Fpurpose-built amusement park with a
OL,13,Fcircus, ballroom, arcade, dining hall,
OL,14,Fbilliard room, zoo and ice rink.
OL,16,FOpened in 1901 and designed by
OL,17,Farchitect George Sherrin, the Grade-II
OL,18,Flisted site today is now occupied by a
OL,19,FTesco Express.
