OL,4,CVictorian building on 'endangered' list
OL,6,FThe location was forced to close in
OL,7,F1986 following an unsuccessful
OL,8,Fcampaign to save the attraction.
OL,10,FThe Jesmond Dene Banqueting Hall in
OL,11,FNewcastle also features on the list.
OL,12,FBuilt by John Dobson in 1860, it was
OL,13,Fexpanded with a gatehouse, reception
OL,14,Fhall and display room by Norman Shaw
OL,15,Fin the following decade.
OL,17,FThe charity said it is now "in a state
OL,18,Fof increasing decay" and may soon be
OL,19,Funable to support the artists who
OL,20,Fcontinue to use it as a studio.
