OL,4,CVictorian building on 'endangered' list
OL,6,FOther buildings on the list include
OL,7,Fone of the first tennis pavilions in
OL,8,Fthe world, a requisitioned school
OL,9,Fwhere author Vera Brittain nursed
OL,10,Fduring the First World War and a
OL,11,FGothic coastal villa in Devon which
OL,12,Fserved as a school for girls from 1885.
OL,14,FSt Martins in Ilfracombe, formerly
OL,15,Fknown as Roslyn Hoe, had become a
OL,16,Fsmall hotel by the 1930s and was
OL,17,Fdescribed by a local architect as an
OL,18,F"exercise in symmetry".
