OL,3,CWorld's first amusement park among
OL,4,CVictorian building on 'endangered' list
OL,6,FEach of the sites listed in need of
OL,7,Frescue and repair are Grade II-listed
OL,8,For above.
OL,10,FThis means they are subject to
OL,11,Fregulations protecting their
OL,12,Fhistorical and architectural
OL,13,Fsignificance, but the charity said it
OL,14,Ffeared this was not enough.
OL,16,FSociety president and comedian Griff
OL,17,FRhys Jones said the list was "a
OL,18,Ftestament to the excitement, variety
OL,19,Fand invention of the Victorian Age".
