OL,3,CWorld's first amusement park among
OL,4,CVictorian building on 'endangered' list
OL,6,F"How terrifying to see buildings I
OL,7,Fhave known, loved or used all my life
OL,8,Fin Southend and Cardiff in need of
OL,9,Frescue," he added.
OL,11,F"Their restoration and reuse make huge
OL,12,Fcommercial sense. They are attractions
OL,13,Fin themselves. They are already
OL,14,Fdestinations. They should be part of
OL,15,Flocal pride.
OL,17,F"What do we want? A parking lot? A
OL,18,Ffaceless block in their place? A slew
OL,19,Fof new carbon pollution? When they
OL,20,Fhave so much colour, continuity and
OL,21,Fhistory on their side already?"
